snippet.title: Keylocker - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The wait is over- Keylocker is available now on PC, Nintendo Switch, PS5, & Xbox Series X|S! ⚡️

Buy the game on your platform of choice today: 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1325040/Keylocker__Turn_Based_Cyberpunk_Action/
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/keylocker-switch/
PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011063
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/keylocker/9mw8t50z9j3c 
Game Page: https://serenityforge.com/games/keylocker

Keylocker is a cyberpunk turn-based rhythm JRPG, in which you play as the singer/songwriter, B0B0. Fuel your moves with the electric power of music on this unforgiving planet via the real-time execution of rhythmic moves! Battle the authorities, unlock the secrets of Saturn, play in your band's concerts, and hack into the network to bring an end to this corrupt system, for better or worse. 🎸🪐
